<field_public_text>:
Enable redirection to CPU of IPv4 frames failing decapsulation checks.

Related parameters:
ANA_L3:VMID:VMID_ENCAP.DECAP_ENA
ANA_L3:VMID:VMID_ENCAP.DECAP_IP_ENCAP_TYPE
